  "text": "From the results to date, we can deduce that specific environmental attributes such as TC G and NDWI have a more significant influence on the SD and distribution than others. This information will be further analysed and implemented into a cluster ensemble algorithm for optimum accuracy classification for future work [CITATION_1] .",
